# IELTS Task 1 地图题（Map）8.0 万能模板（终极版）

地图题是：

# IELTS Task1 最容易拉开差距的题型之一。

因为：

很多人：

只会：

❌ “左边有什么，右边有什么”

真正 Band 8：

# 是“总结变化逻辑”。

你现在已经开始具备：

* modernization thinking
* relocation thinking
* functional change thinking

所以：

下面我给你的：

不是普通模板。

而是：

# 真正 8.0 地图题写作框架。

你以后：

# 直接往里面套内容即可。

---

# 一、地图题本质（超级重要）

地图题：

# 本质不是“描述位置”

而是：

# “总结变化”

考官真正看：

✅ 你是否会：

* summarize changes
* compare old vs new
* describe relocation
* classify transformations

而不是：

❌ 念地图。

---

# 二、地图题 8.0 标准结构

---

# ① Introduction（1句）

改写题目。

---

# 万能模板

## 模板1（最通用）

> The two maps compare the layout of _____ in _____ and how it looks today.

---

## 模板2（更 academic）

> The maps illustrate how _____ has changed between _____ and _____.

---

## 模板3（多时期）

> The diagrams show the development of _____ over the period from _____ to _____.

---

# 三、Overview（最重要）

# 决定 TA 分数

地图题：

# overview 必须写：

✅ 整体变化
✅ 功能变化
✅ 最大变化
✅ 保留部分

---

# 万能8分 Overview模板

---

## 模板1（现代化）

> Overall, the area has undergone significant modernisation and redevelopment over the period.

---

## 模板2（功能变化）

> Overall, the site became less agricultural and more residential/commercial/tourist-oriented.

---

## 模板3（部分保留）

> While several original features remained unchanged, a number of new facilities were introduced.

---

## 模板4（大规模变化）

> Overall, the area was transformed considerably, with many old structures being replaced or relocated.

---

# 四、Body Paragraph（真正核心）

---

# 高分原则：

# 不按地图顺序写！

---

# 低分：

左边...
右边...
上面...

---

# 高分：

# 按“变化类型”分类。

---

# 五、地图题真正的高分分类法（超级重要）

---

# 1. Added Features（新增）

例如：

* parking
* shops
* roads
* houses

---

# 2. Removed Features（删除）

例如：

* forest removed
* farmland disappeared

---

# 3. Relocated Features（移动）

例如：

* barn moved
* school relocated

---

# 4. Converted Features（功能改变）

例如：

* farmland → hotel
* forest → residential area

---

# 六、Body Paragraph 8分模板（直接套）

---

# Body1（旧地图）

## 模板

> In _____, the area was primarily used for _____.

> The northern/southern/eastern/western part of the site contained _____.

> A _____ was located in the _____ corner, while _____ occupied the central area.

> The site was connected by _____.

---

# Body2（新地图）

## 模板

> Today, the area has been transformed considerably.

> The former _____ has been converted into _____.

> Several new facilities, including _____ and _____, have been added.

> In addition, _____ has been relocated to the _____ part of the site.

> Meanwhile, _____ has remained largely unchanged.

---

# 七、地图题真正8分动词系统（必须背）

---

# 1. 新增类

| 普通    | Band 8    |
| ----- | --------- |
| build | construct |
| add   | introduce |
| put   | establish |

---

# 高分句型

> Several new facilities were constructed.

> A new car park was introduced.

---

# 2. 删除类

| 普通        | 高级         |
| --------- | ---------- |
| remove    | demolish   |
| disappear | be removed |

---

# 高分句型

> The old factory was demolished.

> The farmland was removed.

---

# 3. 替换/功能变化（最重要）

| 普通          | 高级                  |
| ----------- | ------------------- |
| change into | convert into        |
| replace     | be replaced by      |
| turn into   | be transformed into |

---

# 高分句型

> The farmland was converted into a residential area.

> The old market was replaced by a shopping centre.

---

# 4. 移动类（地图题超级高频）

| 普通   | 高级       |
| ---- | -------- |
| move | relocate |

---

# 高分句型

> The barn was relocated to the centre of the site.

---

# 5. 保留不变类

| 普通          | 高级               |
| ----------- | ---------------- |
| stay same   | remain unchanged |
| still there | remain in place  |

---

# 高分句型

> The river remained unchanged throughout the period.

---

# 八、地图题空间表达（超级重要）

---

# 方位词（必须会）

| 中文  | 高级表达                |
| --- | ------------------- |
| 北部  | northern section    |
| 南部  | southern area       |
| 中间  | central area        |
| 东北角 | northeastern corner |

---

# 高分句型

> A large park occupied the northeastern part of the site.

---

# 九、地图题真正8分连接词（必须会）

---

# 对比

> By contrast,

> Meanwhile,

> Whereas...

---

# 补充

> In addition,

> Furthermore,

> Moreover,

---

# 结果

> Consequently,

> As a result,

---

# 十、地图题真正的8分思维（最关键）

很多人：

# “描述地图”

真正高分：

# “总结变化逻辑”

---

# 低分：

> There was a barn.

---

# 高分：

> The agricultural function of the area was reduced significantly.

---

# 低分：

> A road was added.

---

# 高分：

> Accessibility was improved through the construction of roads.

---

# 十一、地图题万能高分句型（直接背）

---

# 总体变化

> The area underwent significant transformation over the period.

---

# 功能变化

> The site became increasingly residential/commercial/tourist-oriented.

---

# 替换

> The former farmland was converted into a residential complex.

---

# 新增

> Several new facilities were introduced.

---

# 移动

> The school was relocated to the western side of the area.

---

# 不变

> The river remained unchanged.

---

# 十二、地图题最容易犯的错误（非常重要）

---

# 1. 流水账

❌：

左边...
右边...

---

# 2. 没有 overview

地图题：

# 没 overview 很难7+。

---

# 3. 不总结变化

只写：

“有什么”

不写：

# “变成什么”

---

# 4. 不分类变化

高分：

一定会：

* add
* remove
* relocate
* convert

分类。

---

# 十三、真正8分地图题完整模板（直接套）

---

# Introduction

> The two maps compare the layout of _____ in _____ and how it looks today.

---

# Overview

> Overall, the area has undergone significant redevelopment and modernisation. While several original features have remained unchanged, many new facilities have been introduced and some areas have been converted for different purposes.

---

# Body1（过去）

> In _____, the area was mainly used for _____. The northern section contained _____, while _____ was located in the southern part. In addition, _____ connected different parts of the site.

---

# Body2（现在）

> Today, the site has changed considerably. The former _____ has been converted into _____. Several new facilities, including _____ and _____, have also been constructed. Meanwhile, _____ has remained largely unchanged, although _____ has been relocated to the central area.

---

# 十四、真正的Band 8地图题核心（最后一句）

真正高分地图题：

# 不是“描述位置”

而是：

# “总结区域功能变化”。
